DESCRIPTION:Want to get more involved this summer including helping out at
  outreach events\, group rides\, and election organizing? We’re hosting 
 a virtual volunteer orientation session on Wednesday\, May 20th.\n\nWe wil
 l cover various topics including\, but not limited to\, the basics of our 
 organization\, our different outreach programs and advocacy campaigns\, an
 d how you as a volunteer can help bolster our efforts in the coming weeks 
 and months.\n\nRSVP for Zoom link.\nURL: https://www.cycleto.ca/volunteer_
 orientation_20260520
LOCATION:Zoom
URL:https://www.cycleto.ca/volunteer_orientation_20260520
END:VEVENT
