BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Bike Match Drop Off at Dufferin Grove Farmers' Market
DTSTART:20260528T190000Z
DTEND:20260528T223000Z
DTSTAMP:20260519T065516Z
UID:30e36bb2-5706-5a9a-87c9-cec1efc7dde0
DESCRIPTION:Cycle Toronto is collecting bike donations at the Dufferin Gro
 ve Farmers' Market on Thursday\, May 28 from 3:00 PM - 6:30 PM.\n\nAll don
 ated bikes go toward our Bike Match program\, which was founded by Women's
  Cycling Network and aims to increase access to cycling across the city wh
 ile giving donated bikes a second life.\n\nCycle Toronto and our partner b
 ike hubs collect donated bicycles\, repair them\, and provide them to comm
 unity members in need. Interested participants can sign up through the (ht
 tps://bikematchwcn.com/) Bike Match website.\nURL: https://www.cycleto.ca/
 engagement_station_at_dufferin_grove_farmers_market
LOCATION:
URL:https://www.cycleto.ca/engagement_station_at_dufferin_grove_farmers_ma
 rket
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Evergreen Brick Works Community Ride
DTSTART:20260613T140000Z
DTEND:20260613T160000Z
DTSTAMP:20260519T065516Z
UID:3dee8ecb-efee-518d-ad9b-16b95489e8c3
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Bike Month with a Community Ride! This year\, our ri
 de starts and ends at Cycle Toronto's new Rec Hub at Evergreen Brick Works
 .\n\n* Date: Saturday\, June 13\n* Time: Meeting time 10:00 am\, departure
  time 10:30. Back at Cycle Toronto Rec Hub (Evergreen Brick Works) at 12:0
 0 pm\n* Location: 550 Bayview Avenue\, Toronto ON\, M4W 3X8\n* Route: http
 s://ridewithgps.com/routes/54801489\n\nDon’t own a bike? No problem!\n\n
 Our partners at Bike Share Toronto will be providing a LIMITED NUMBER OF C
 OMPLIMENTARY bikes at the new Cycle Toronto Rec Hub (550 Bayview Ave).\n\n
 SIGN UP IS REQUIRED - Please fill out this (https://docs.google.com/forms/
 d/e/1FAIpQLSdRjz_HJGPbdOE3z1mYFLWQQM2b_cJdHwyeb0N5nODp_Ze2WQ/viewform?usp=
 publish-editor) form if you are interested in borrowing a Bike Share bike 
 for the ride.\nURL: https://www.cycleto.ca/evergreen_brick_works_community
 _ride
LOCATION:Evergreen Brick Works\n550 Bayview Avenue\nToronto ON M4W 3X8\nCA
URL:https://www.cycleto.ca/evergreen_brick_works_community_ride
END:VEVENT
